libQTidy
------------------------------------------
A library and some helper programs that make it easier  
to integrate Tidy in Qt Applications.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  libqscintilla2_4-2.3-1
  libQtCore4-4.4.1-1
  libQtDBus4-4.4.1-1
  libQtGui4-4.4.1-1
  libQtNetwork4-4.4.1-1
  libQtXml4-4.4.1-1
  libtidy0_99_0-20080811-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.4.0-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  gcc-g++-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1

Canonical website:
  http://qtidy.hjcms.de/

Canonical download:
  http://qtidy.hjcms.de/Downloads/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack libQTidy-0.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./libQTidy-0.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libQTidy-0.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libQTidy-0.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libQTidy-devel-0.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libQTidy0-0.2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary packages:

  /etc/postinstall/libQTidy.sh
  /usr/bin/qtidyrc.exe
  /usr/bin/qtidyxml.exe
  /usr/share/applications/qtidyrc.desktop
  /usr/share/doc/libQTidy-0.2.0/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libQTidy-0.2.0/COPYING.LIB
  /usr/share/doc/libQTidy-0.2.0/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libQTidy-0.2.0/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libQTidy-0.2.0/README
  /usr/share/pixmaps/qtidyrc.png

(libQTidy0)
  /usr/bin/cygQTidy-0.dll
  /usr/share/qtidy/COPYING
  /usr/share/qtidy/COPYING.lib
  /usr/share/qtidy/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/qtidy/NEWS
  /usr/share/qtidy/README
  /usr/share/qtidy/qtidyrc_untranslated.ts
  /usr/share/qtidy/tidy.conf
  /usr/share/qtidy/tidy.dtd
  /usr/share/qtidy/tidy.xml

(libQTidy-devel)
  /usr/include/qt4/QTidy/QTidy
  /usr/include/qt4/QTidy/QTidy.h
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/QTidy.pc
  /usr/lib/qt4/lib/libQTidy.dll.a

